Lunixs Notes
--------------
User Name : root 
password : root123

-----------------
get Server id : hostname -I (Capital I)

if Logins with git bash or commed prompt : ssh root@192.168.20.128

IP Address : hostname -I
================
OPEN LUNIX FOLLOWED THINGS:
-----------------------------------

Lunix Home Directory : cd /
Lunix list : ls
============
Lunix free Directory : cd /opt/ (opt, tmp free directory)
Create file : touch file /CAT, VI (Total 18 Ways)
See Total list : ll, ls -l

If Go to directary : cd dir1/
Present where you are : pwd (Present working Directory)

If Go to More directary : cd dir1/dir2/dir3/
One Step back : cd ..
More Steps : cd ../../..
Recent to Old : ls -lt
Old to recent : ls -ltr (list of time recorcively)
Create Hiden File : .file (".file name")
See Hidden file : ls -a OR ls -la

Create file : touch file
Delete file : rm file (rm "filename")
Create directory : mkdir dir1
Delete directory : rmdir dir (rmdir "file name")

Perminente delete directory : rm -rf dir
Perminente delete file: rm -rf file

Create Nested Directory : mkdir -p dir1/dir2/dir3/dir4 (dir1 into create dir2 as well as)
=================
CAT
-----------------------
Create cat file : cate > file 1 hello all 
Save cate : ctrl+d

view data : cat file
Add New Data cat : cat >> file 1  hello all  all hello (Both shown)
Replace Data : cat > file 1
==============
Go to file : vi file
Add any data : esc i
save file : esc:w!
Close : :q!
========
Coomand line mode : esc

-----------
dd - delete a line
ndd - no.of lines delete
yy - copy a line
p - paste
nyy - no.of lines copy
p - paste
dw - delete a word
ndw - delete no.of words
x - char delete
$ - end of the line
^ - starting of the line
o - create a new line below the couser
O - above the couser

G - ground
H - head
a - append




